1
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:52,970
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,550 --> 00:00:56,070
[Episode 8]

3
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,500
Leave me alone.

4
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,640
Useless men.

5
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,470
Who are you calling useless?

6
00:01:03,470 --> 00:01:04,330
Us, obviously.

7
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:06,790
Whatever I, Huang Shang, want to do,

8
00:01:06,790 --> 00:01:07,790
I will get it done.

9
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,400
Our family of witches

10
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,590
has been guarding the town
for generations.

11
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:12,720
I don't believe that

12
00:01:12,870 --> 00:01:13,840
I can't handle

13
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:15,350
a small demon myself.

14
00:01:16,230 --> 00:01:16,680
Demon!

15
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,660
Don't yell.

16
00:01:17,789 --> 00:01:18,650
Show yourself!

17
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,039
Demon!

18
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,230
Don't yell.

19
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:22,230
Where is the demon?

20
00:01:22,230 --> 00:01:22,710
Demon!

21
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,140
Show yourself!

22
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,210
Demon...

23
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:34,479
Why is there a butterfly

24
00:01:34,509 --> 00:01:35,640
flying around at night?

25
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,700
Such a big one, too.

26
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,150
There's nothing.

27
00:01:39,229 --> 00:01:40,870
So it's... A demon?

28
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,090
Bai Xiaonian!

29
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:21,010
In... In the East,
the green demon of pestilence,

30
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,710
spirit of rotten wood.

31
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,550
In the South,

32
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,150
the red demon of pestilence,

33
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:26,440
spirit of flame.

34
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:28,190
In the West...

35
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,180
Biyun, you're back.

36
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,040
You're back.

37
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:38,960
Let go of me!

38
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:40,280
You jerk!

39
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:42,680
Biyun.

40
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:44,450
Don't you remember me?

41
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,190
Who is Biyun?

42
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:49,430
Bi- Biyun?

43
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,240
Huang Biyun?

44
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,000
You're not Biyun.

45
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,210
Then where is Biyun now?

46
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,590
Huang Biyun?

47
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,220
She is my great-grandmother.

48
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,770
Your great-grandmother?

49
00:03:02,900 --> 00:03:03,310
Then she must be

50
00:03:03,310 --> 00:03:05,110
from almost a hundred years ago.

51
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:08,110
She

52
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,960
was a mortal.

53
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:11,960
It's been almost a hundred years.

54
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,890
She's long gone.

55
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:24,630
Biyun...

56
00:03:29,050 --> 00:03:29,540
Is gone?

57
00:03:29,950 --> 00:03:32,480
[Many years ago]

58
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,079
Are you there?

59
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,250
I know you are there.

60
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,840
Hiding is useless.

61
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,310
I am a witch.

62
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,390
I can feel your demonic aura.

63
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,840
Look, this is plum blossom.

64
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,080
Have you seen it?

65
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,280
It's very pretty.

66
00:04:03,590 --> 00:04:04,850
Unlike your mountain,

67
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,030
which is so barren.

68
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,360
I'll leave if you don't come out.

69
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,290
I will leave

70
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:16,250
this plum blossom branch for you.

71
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,850
I'll come find you when I have time.

72
00:04:20,010 --> 00:04:22,520
Remember, my name is Huang Biyun.

73
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,480
I'm leaving.

74
00:04:24,390 --> 00:04:26,190
Don't come looking for me again.

75
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,120
You spoke to me!

76
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,430
It's my first time hearing your voice.

77
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,750
Let me see your face,

78
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:33,360
okay?

79
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,360
So afraid of seeing people.

80
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,720
Are you very ugly?

81
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:40,640
You're the ugly one.

82
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:43,070
Everyone in town says I'm pretty.

83
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,159
You run fast.

84
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:58,190
You ugly girl.

85
00:04:58,950 --> 00:04:59,680
The people in your town

86
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,480
are all liars.

87
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,600
Ugly girl.

88
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,870
Don't come looking for me again.

89
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,150
Are you there?

90
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,080
The red plum branch I gave you

91
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,890
has almost grown into a forest,

92
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,670
but I've yet to see your face.

93
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,040
Grandma said that

94
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,570
in a few days,

95
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,130
a great disaster will come.

96
00:05:45,290 --> 00:05:46,110
I need a spirit beast

97
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:47,720
to protect my town with me.

98
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,330
It's been so many years.

99
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:53,040
I come to beg you every year.

100
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,830
Why won't you ever agree?

101
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,530
Because you are not pretty.

102
00:05:59,390 --> 00:05:59,990
Ugly girl.

103
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,360
There's a custom in our town.

104
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,920
When the red plum blossoms bloom,

105
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:14,480
girls will tie red strings
on the branches.

106
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,680
Soon, they will get to marry

107
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,480
a good man.

108
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,900
Are you going to get married?

109
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,980
You're so ugly,

110
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:22,840
who would want to marry you?

111
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:24,390
Nonsense.

112
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,830
I'm not ugly at all.

113
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:38,560
I figure that

114
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,430
the red plum blossoms here

115
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,120
have absorbed your spiritual energy,

116
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:45,320
so they should be more effective
than the ones in our town.

117
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,320
You have to bless me, too.

118
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:15,690
Ha! You fell for it!

119
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,340
This demon-binding rope

120
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:18,040
was made specifically for you

121
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,950
by my own hands.

122
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:20,470
Now you can't escape.

123
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:21,800
Calling me ugly?

124
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:22,480
Let me see

125
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,060
if you look any better.

126
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,750
You call me ugly every day,

127
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:34,120
but you're not that good-looking either.

128
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,980
You tricked me.

129
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:37,190
You humans are so shameless!

130
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:38,720
So stubborn.

131
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:40,800
Since I caught you,

132
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,870
you are my spirit beast.

133
00:07:41,870 --> 00:07:42,950
If you don't listen,

134
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:43,810
I will beat you.

135
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,550
I can even kill you right now.

136
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,460
From now on,

137
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,830
I am your master.

138
00:07:52,070 --> 00:07:52,870
In the future,

139
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,920
you will be our town's

140
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,250
guardian spirit beast.

141
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,630
If you refuse,

142
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,950
I'll extract your inner core

143
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:01,000
and destroy your cultivation.

144
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,120
As for your true form,

145
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,920
I could send it to

146
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,800
an acrobatics troupe

147
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,630
to be a sideshow.

148
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:05,600
I'll kill you!

149
00:08:06,650 --> 00:08:07,780
You can't even move.

150
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,750
What's your name?

151
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:13,640
Speak.

152
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,270
Bai Lin!

153
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:18,950
So, you're called Bai Lin.

154
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,830
So Huang Biyun

155
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,970
brought you back

156
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,010
and sealed you in that well.

157
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,690
You're also stupid.

158
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,240
For so many years,

159
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,600
she went looking for you every year.

160
00:08:34,669 --> 00:08:35,840
She was a witch;

161
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:37,549
she was bound to find a way

162
00:08:37,549 --> 00:08:38,789
to capture you one day.

163
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:40,390
Yet you stayed there every year.

164
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:42,650
Weren't you just waiting to be captured?

165
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,490
Living here all by yourself

166
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,680
must have been very lonely.

167
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,440
Actually,

168
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:58,080
I hoped she would visit every year.

169
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,630
I lied.

170
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,340
She was not ugly at all.

171
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:08,600
She was beautiful since childhood.

172
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,260
I was so happy she captured me.

173
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,480
She said

174
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,240
she wanted me to join her

175
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,500
in guarding this town.

176
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,400
I was very happy too.

177
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,310
She said the land of China

178
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:23,470
was facing a great disaster.

179
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,500
I wanted to watch over the town

180
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,440
together with her.

181
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,270
Your great-grandmother...

182
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,080
Didn't she go to Nanyang?

183
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:39,680
Nanyang?

184
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,530
Wasn't it a town over the mountain?

185
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:04,210
Why did you break the barrier?

186
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:06,560
Aren't you afraid I'd run away?

187
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,040
I'm leaving.

188
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:14,160
Father is taking our whole family
to Nanyang.

189
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:15,400
This way,

190
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,130
when I'm not around,

191
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,700
you can still come out.

192
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,120
You are my spirit beast.

193
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,120
When I'm gone,

194
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,100
you must protect this town for me.

195
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:26,910
Where is Nanyang?

196
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,560
Is it another town?

197
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,240
Yes.

198
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,270
It's

199
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:33,610
on the other side of the mountain.

200
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:34,670
Just another town.

201
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,770
Then how many days will you be gone?

202
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,510
Bai Lin.

203
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,250
When I'm not around,

204
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,670
can you

205
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,200
watch over this town for me?

206
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,840
Are you going to get married?

207
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,370
What are you talking about?

208
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,600
Who'd get married

209
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,810
at a time like this?

210
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:57,600
Okay, I promise you.

211
00:10:58,610 --> 00:10:59,670
Before you return,

212
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,450
I will guard this town for you.

213
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:14,870
Bai Lin.

214
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:19,080
I...

215
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,010
Bai Lin.

216
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,900
Wait for my return.

217
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,130
You must wait for my return.

218
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:39,650
I waited for her for a long time.

219
00:11:43,150 --> 00:11:45,350
So long that this town became deserted,

220
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:51,000
yet she still hadn't returned.

221
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:52,480
Actually,

222
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,270
by untying that rope,

223
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,200
she set you free.

224
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,050
You could have left at any time.

225
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,070
I promised her

226
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,920
to protect this town.

227
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:04,930
A promise is a promise.

228
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:16,770
Let me tell you.

229
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,270
My

230
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,880
great-grandmother's father,

231
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,630
who is my...

232
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,260
Never mind.

233
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:28,840
Her whole family
moved to Nanyang for business

234
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:31,390
and never returned to China.

235
00:12:32,150 --> 00:12:33,910
As for my great-grandmother...

236
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:35,310
After 3 years in Nanyang,

237
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:36,630
her father found her a Chinese man

238
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:37,720
to marry into the family

239
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:39,120
as a live-in son-in-law.

240
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,080
Then,

241
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:42,410
she gave birth to my grandmother.

242
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,140
Many years later,

243
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,870
I was born.

244
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,600
Bai Lin,

245
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,390
thank you

246
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,400
for protecting this town

247
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,440
for our family

248
00:12:58,910 --> 00:13:00,240
for so many years.

249
00:13:01,450 --> 00:13:02,360
My great-grandmother

250
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,820
has been gone from this world
for a long time.

251
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,170
You are free.

252
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,760
I have decided

253
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,240
to give up developing this town.

254
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:14,220
After all, you have protected it

255
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:15,220
for so many years.

256
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,170
From now on,

257
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:18,150
I will protect it for you.

258
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:21,360
I can go?

259
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,000
But where can I go?

260
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:34,950
Right.

261
00:13:38,510 --> 00:13:38,960
This

262
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,200
was passed down from my great-grandmother

263
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,150
to me.

264
00:13:43,870 --> 00:13:44,930
I'll give it to you.

265
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:47,670
You can

266
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,160
keep it as a memento.

267
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:53,360
This is

268
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:56,930
what I gave to Biyun

269
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,080
when we parted.

270
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:04,960
Wait.

271
00:14:08,110 --> 00:14:09,510
I have something for you.

272
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,840
Keep it with you.

273
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:18,630
I have never been to
the other side of the mountain.

274
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,480
I don't know if there are any

275
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,810
powerful demons there.

276
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,970
If you are in danger,

277
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,180
it can protect you.

278
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,530
You must come back quickly,

279
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:29,840
Biyun.

280
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,330
What is that?

281
00:14:39,030 --> 00:14:40,490
It's Bai Lin's inner core.

282
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:04,370
Biyun!

283
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,440
Is that

284
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:10,840
my great-grandmother?

285
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:12,790
It's Huang Biyun's soul,

286
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,940
attached to Bai Lin's inner core.

287
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,240
She came back.

288
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:23,580
I knew you would come back.

289
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:25,790
Bai Lin.

290
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:29,810
This place doesn't need
our protection anymore.

291
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:33,840
This time,

292
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:35,770
I'll go with you

293
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:38,080
to your world.

294
00:15:39,610 --> 00:15:41,210
I will never leave you again.

295
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:18,900
Are you kidding me?

296
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,850
She made him a spirit beast?

297
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:21,630
He's...

298
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,200
A dragon?

299
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:27,690
A deep yearning hidden
in 10 years of encounter.

300
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:30,840
A century of waiting
reflects deep affection.

301
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,360
She entrusted her freedom.

302
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:37,240
He answered with time.

303
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:40,950
A promise is an unspoken contract.

304
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:46,240
Waiting is gentleness
etched into the soul.

305
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:51,240
So romantic.

306
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:52,960
The witch

307
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:56,080
and her demon's love is so touching.

308
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:57,430
Ms. Huang,

309
00:16:58,030 --> 00:17:00,160
I didn't expect a strong woman like you

310
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,390
would shed tears.

311
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:02,960
Thank you.

312
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,170
You're welcome.

313
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:06,250
Well, generally speaking,

314
00:17:06,849 --> 00:17:08,000
dragons are not considered demons,

315
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,510
and they wouldn't be
a human's spirit beast.

316
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:11,240
It's because they fell in love.

317
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:15,270
So,

318
00:17:16,109 --> 00:17:17,040
Bai Lin has left?

319
00:17:21,069 --> 00:17:21,920
This town

320
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,260
can actually still be developed.

321
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:26,800
How can you go back on your word?

322
00:17:27,810 --> 00:17:29,070
I was just considering

323
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,340
the dragon's feelings just now.

324
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,400
You already promised him.

325
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,310
This isn't very good, is it?

326
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:33,070
No, wait.

327
00:17:33,070 --> 00:17:33,920
Forget about those.

328
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:35,350
Ms. Huang, do you remember?

329
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:36,200
At that time, you gave us

330
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,310
a 100,000 yuan reward.

331
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:38,510
We gave it back to you.

332
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,270
You should give it back to us now.

333
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,160
What role

334
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,570
did you two play?

335
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,850
You men are useless.

336
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,160
Why don't you two

337
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,620
get me a spirit beast, too?

338
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:49,640
I also want a dragon.

339
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:50,200
A dragon?

340
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,150
From where?

341
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:52,310
Do I look like a dragon to you?

342
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,110
Get one for me.

343
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:54,640
Waiting for a hero.

344
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:55,680
I am that dragon.

345
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:56,200
No.

346
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,680
We worked so hard.

347
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,070
You have to give us what we deserve.

348
00:17:59,070 --> 00:18:00,330
You were completely useless.

349
00:18:00,330 --> 00:18:00,920
Ms. Huang!

